   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The AB9006 is a link between two industrial networks. On the Modbus-TCP
network, it function as client and as server on the EtherNet/IP network.</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Fast copying of cyclic I/O data between a Modbus TCP and an
EtherNet/IP network (5 ms)</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Max I/O data capacity of 256 bytes in each direction</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Robust stand-alone housing for use in harsh industrial environments</p>
         </li>
